songs.title: Doctor’s Office
songs.lyrics:
Yes may I help you?

Hello I had a 12:00 appointment with Dr. Dre

Well Dr. Dre is with another patient right now
Would you like to reschedule?

Reschedule? Um it must be a mistake
I must see him I had a 12:00 appointment

No it’s no mistake
Look Dr. Dre is with another patient either you can wait or reschedule

Look I understand all of that. But...

No apparently you don’t understand...

You know I’m a workin' person &...

& I work too

Just where is Dr. Dre?
I need to see him

Well open up the door & you’ll see his big dick fuckin' somebody!

::Moaning::
Give it to me!
Give it to me!
::Moaning::
